{"tid":2064982,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[樓市gogogo] 天晉四房2100萬沽 創屋苑同類新高","createTime":"2020-06-15T08:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T15:16:16.000Z","uid":339805,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2a82a28c0adb5ea44744fef29c65aca5e06883bf","tid":2064982,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:10:17.000Z","msg":"將軍澳日出康城SEA TO SKY開價在即，區內續錄二手成交，其中天晉錄得6月首宗成交，有4房單位成交價創同類新高紀錄。中原高級分區營業董事伍錦基指，天晉第1座高層C室，實用968方呎4房1套間隔、享海景，原業主於今年初叫價2200萬元放盤，新近以2100萬元沽出，減幅為100萬元或4.5%，實呎21694元，成交價為屋苑同類新高價。<br />\n <br />\n資料顯示，屋苑8座高層C室，實用968方呎，曾於2017年6月以2090萬元易手。換言之，上述最新成交價較舊紀錄高出10萬元或0.5%。原業主2012年5月以1447.8萬元買入單位，持貨8年，帳面獲利652.2萬元或45%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1592205148946&amp;issue=20200615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1592205148946%26issue%3D20200615&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8gwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=2fae59a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1592205148946&amp;issue=20200615</a>"},{"pid":"9c6d10f32faeca91d66c958c83bd37518844c561","tid":2064982,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:26:27.000Z","msg":"唔係跌緊架咩聽連登仔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824819405e14abd1901e53d41f1894485960ac70","tid":2064982,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:31:27.000Z","msg":"有病睇醫生"},{"pid":"a005794568f691922885462ee891a22ba92dc2ef","tid":2064982,"uid":73269,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:32:09.000Z","msg":"假新聞,左手交右手幫房地產商造勢"},{"pid":"5f1e3305cdff735643d4f51dcdbbfbac2fe6ca72","tid":2064982,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"16